A sporty and powerful electric bike

The Aries combines a unique, supple, full-suspension frame designed to take on any road or trail, with wider tires to help absorb any bumps along the way. The available SuperCharged 500W motor makes climbing hills a breeze, while the balanced weight distribution afforded by our patented mid-drive motor results in more responsive handling.




