Shifting Gears Is As Easy As Turning A Dial
NuVinci® makes manual shifting a thing of the past with its continuous variable transmission. Watch the display simulate the terrain you are on as you turn a dial to smoothly shift gears. It is intuitive with no learning curve. Best of all, NuVinci® systems require no regular maintenance.











The Power to Conquer Any Hill
Our powerful mid-drive motor means that hills are no longer an obstacle when you ride. Locating the motor in the middle of the frame, closer to the bike’s center of gravity, ensures improved handling and safer riding. All EVELOs are equipped with both pedal-assist and throttle functionality. You can pedal as little or as much as you want, while the throttle lets you take a break from pedaling or can give you an extra boost up hills. Either way − pedal-assist or throttle −  you are always in control.











Go The Extra Mile
If you plan to take your electric bike on a longer trip than usual, we have you covered. Our standard batteries have a range of up to 40 miles. The optional extended-range batteries, available on some models, increase that range to up to 60 miles per charge. All of our bikes have high-quality batteries from manufacturers such as Panasonic, Samsung, and Lenovo. Ride and explore, while spending less time wondering if you have enough power to get back home!











