SpecsClick to see details







Motor
Patented Brushless Motor, 250W Continuous/400W Peak OR 500W Continuous/750W Peak



Battery
Lithium Polymer 36V10Ah, 48V10Ah or 48V14.5Ah, depending on model



Charger
36V or 48V 110-220V Lithium Battery Charger (4-6 hours for a full charge)



Maximum Motor-Assisted Speed
20 miles per hour (can be increased to 25 MPH in off-road mode with SuperCharged 500W Motor)



Range
Estimated 40 miles on pedal-assist or 20 miles on electric-only (30-60 miles with 48V14.5Ah battery)



Electric Assist
Multiple levels, plus electric-only (via throttle)



Frame
Aluminum Alloy Dual-Suspension.  The 250W model includes a rear spring coil shock (HTL-620); 500W models are equipped with an A5 Kind Air Shock.



Fork
RockShox XC28



Wheel
26” Inch



Tire
Kenda – 26″ x 1.95″



Brakes
Avid BB5 Mechanical Disc Brake







