Lights
Spanninga Front & Rear Lights



Speedometer
LCD Speedometer by Kingmeter



Fender
All-Weather Front Fender



Rear Rack
Full-Size



Bicycle Weight (without battery)
59 pounds (61 pounds with NuVinci)



Battery Weight
36V10Ah – 8 pounds; 48V10Ah – 8 pounds; 48V14.5Ah – 9 pounds










