Leisure Products

Company Overview of EVELO Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
EVELO Inc. manufactures electric bicycles. It offers its products directly, as well as online in the United States and Canada. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in New York, New York.


327 Beach 101st StreetFloor 4New York, NY 10014United StatesFounded in 2012



Phone: 877-991-7272

www.evelo.com







