Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Leisure Products
Sub-Industry: Sporting Goods
Evelo Inc. of Washington provides recreational products. The Company offers electric bicycles, parts, accessories, and repair services. Evelo serves customers in the United States and Canada.




