A stylish & comfortable electric cruiser

Luna is our take on the classic cruiser bike, and we’ve designed it to be perfect for more than just the beachfront boardwalk. The deep step-through frame provides super-easy on-and-off access, while the swept-back handlebars keep the rider in an upright sitting position. Its well-designed seat combines support with maximum comfort. No wonder it is popular with both men and women. With exceptional cargo capacity, an optional 500W motor, and available NuVinci® fully automatic transmission, Luna can take you just about anywhere!




