Quick & easy assembly
We can ship your electric bike to your doorstep anywhere in the country. It arrives almost fully assembled (95%), so you can be riding in no time! Want to see how easy the assembly is? Watch this short 5 minute video.




















How does service work?
If you have a technical issue at any time, the service process is quite simple. Just report the issue via our website or give us a call. We have customer service agents available 7 days a week and will respond within 24 hours.
















