We've Perfected the Electric Bike
Our advantage? A 60 mile range, automatic gear shifting, and ultra-powerful mid-drive motor design


        EVELO electric bikes were designed  to replace cars for short-distance commuting and enhance biking for recreation, while our exclusive Omni Wheel turns any bike into an electric bike in less than 30 minutes. 
  


 










ARIES

              Conquer your ride with the high-performance, powerful Aries.          



AURORA

              Front suspension hybrid commuter perfect for any occasion.          



LUNA

Easy-going cruiser with step-through frame for style & comfort.            



ORION

The perfect city bike – for getting to work or around town.              







The Omni Wheel Makes Any Bike Electric
Allows us to tackle the existing market

The Omni Wheel is designed to fit practically any bicycle or lifestyle. Whether you have a cruiser, an urban city bike, a recumbent, or anything in-between, once you install the Omni Wheel, your bike becomes an electric hybrid.           
How it Works

Omni Wheel complements your own pedal power. With a throttle providing power on demand, you can pedal as much or as little as you want – while always having the power from the wheel available at the push of a button.          












The E-Bike Industry is Rapidly Expanding
Electric bikes help people to overcome barriers like hills, distance, and fitness levels and enjoy cycling for both recreation and for their commute.

      The electric bike has made biking more accessible than ever to a whole generation of older riders and long-distance commuters. This industry is just beginning.
    



