Europe is already on board. The US market is about to take off
We're reaching a new market of commuters and bike enthusiasts here in the US and abroad. EVELO is riding the wave of an entirely new industry.




"I would guess 90 to 95 percent of people in the U.S. don’t even know what an electric bicycle is.”- Ryan Citron, Navigant Analyst




"It’s a category that is wide open. Little guys are jumping into a business that no one's been paying attention to." - Edward Benjamin, Senior Managing Director of ECycleElectric Consultants


 



"The U.S. market could develop “way faster” than Europe’s did."- Claus Fleischer, Head of Bosch’s E-bike Division




"Electrics “finally have legs to be able to take off in the U.S.,” because cyclists are feeling safer on the roads, battery and motor technology is improving, and retail prices are dropping. - Todd Grant, President of the National Bike Dealers Association





Read more in this Bloomberg Businessweek Article



Disrupting the Bike Industry Via Direct-to-Consumer Distribution
We ship directly to the consumer, eliminating distribution costs and inflated markups.

The bicycle industry’s distribution model is antiquated. For every bike sold, wholesalers and dealers may add hundreds of dollars (40-60%) to the end price tag the consumer pays.
EVELO cuts out the middleman by delivering the bike directly to your door. With test rides provided through our Ambassador Program, we provide quality customer support with hassle-free delivery.
  


SALES AMBASSADORS

     Pairs potential buyers with existing customers for test rides and feature explanations, just like bike shops provide.
  



PRE-ASSEMBLED

             Arrives at your doorstep 95% assembled. The finishing touches will take no more than 30 minutes.
        



FREE RETURNS

The industry’s first 10-Day At-Home Trial policy. Try it at home for 10 days for a risk-free experience.
          



SERVICES & REPAIRS

We contact a partner bike shop near your home. Just drop off the bike at the shop, we take it from there.         



Our Network of Ambassadors Covers the Nation
Our Ambassador Program replaces dealers by connecting existing EVELO owners with potential customers for test-rides. Our Ambassadors (existing owners) make money every time they do a test-ride and every time that test ride turns into a sale. As such, we are the only company of its kind where our customers can actually earn an income off their bike.






On Track to Make $3M this Year
 We reached $1 million of sales in Q2 2016 and have grown 60-70% year over year. 
Since launching in 2011, our growth has far exceeded our own expectations.



Since launching in 2011, our growth has been electric. We’ve made $6 million in revenue since inception in 2011 and $1 million in sales the past three months alone. We're on track to exceed $3 million this year. 
  





