We’re Revolutionizing Bike Riding and Bike Buying

Now, we're ready to ramp up production and introduce new products.




May 2012

The Original Product Line
Boris & Yevgeniy Mordkovich launch EVELO to make urban transportation better and cycling more accessible to more people.



January 2014

The Ambassador Program
Launched the industry's first Ambassador Program so that existing customers can earn money from showing their bike to others, while helping EVELO bypass the traditional brick-and-mortar route.



 August 2014

